===Adjective===
{{en-adj|-}}

# Sexually attracted or open to all people regardless of [[gender]], [[gender identity]], or [[sexual orientation]].
#* {{quote-journal|1995|October 11|Owen McNally|The Vigor, Venom and Wit of Gore Vidal|Hartford Courant|page=E1|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courant/access/22919641.html?dids=22919641:22919641&FMT=ABS|passage=As a writer/sexologist, he argues that people are neither homosexual nor heterosexual but '''pansexual'''.}}
